text:
Hey all, I asked this in another channel but am trying my luck here, too: I’m creating a dnd footer partial for a theme and none of the modules included in the dnd code are showing in the global content editor. I’ve been digging through the internet and HubSpot for possible solutions, but am hitting a wall. Does anyone know why my footer partial wouldn’t be rendering on any pages or in the global content editor? Thanks! Here’s my footer code:
```&lt;!--
  templateType: global_partial
  label: Footer
--&gt;

&lt;footer class="footer"&gt;
  {% dnd_area 'footer' class='footer__container content-wrapper', label='Footer' %}

    {# Main section #}
    {% dnd_section %}
      {% dnd_column %}
        {% dnd_row %}
          {% dnd_module 'site_logo' path='@HubSpot/logo' align='center' %}
          {% end_dnd_module %}
        {% end_dnd_row %}
        {% dnd_row
          margin={
          'top': 12,
          'bottom': 12
          }
        %}
          {% dnd_module path='@HubSpot/rich_text' %}
            {% module_attribute 'html' %}
              &lt;div style="text-align: center; font-size: 1rem;"&gt;
                &lt;p style="color: #949494;"&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Maecenas fringilla consectetur metus at scelerisque. Nam mattis felis quis sollicitudin cursus. Suspendisse potenti. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
                  &lt;a href=""&gt;Privacy Policy&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=""&gt;Terms &amp; Conditions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            {% end_module_attribute %}
          {% end_dnd_module %}
        {% end_dnd_row %}
        {% dnd_row %}
          {% dnd_module path='@HubSpot/rich_text' %}
            {% module_attribute 'html' %}
              &lt;div style="text-align: center; font-size: 1rem;"&gt;
                &lt;span style="color: #949494;"&gt;© Copyright {{ year }} <http://YourBrand.com|YourBrand.com> — All rights reserved&lt;/span&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            {% end_module_attribute %}
          {% end_dnd_module %}
        {% end_dnd_row %}
      {% end_dnd_column %}
    {% end_dnd_section %}
    {# Main section #}

  {% end_dnd_area %}
&lt;/footer&gt;```
